       H-MIZUG			       SECTION.
      *---------------------------------------------------------------*
       H00.
	    PERFORM DZA-ATCHALAT-MIZUG.
	    PERFORM D10-AVODA UNTIL SW-SOF-MIZUG.
	    PERFORM DZZ-SIYOM-MIZUG.
       H-EXIT. EXIT.
