	    IF NOT MH-KM-FILE-STATUS-TAKIN
		   DISPLAY '•…— š‡‰š” „Œ—š'
		   STOP RUN.
	    PERFORM DB-KRIAT-TORAN VARYING I-TORAN FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL
	     I-TORAN > 2.
	    PERFORM DC-BCHIRAT-TORAN.
       HZA-EXIT. EXIT.
